sources.description:
Enslaved Hobbits Fight For Freedom | The Hobbit War | Full Fantasy Movie - In a dark age, the gentle Hobbits are torn from their homes and enslaved by the fearsome Java Men, dragon-riding fiends who feast on flesh and fear. Young Goben, small in size but fierce in heart, must rally his people and strike an uneasy alliance with the towering humans to fight back. Through scorched lands, treacherous mountains, and dragon fire, Goben leads a desperate rebellion, risking everything to reclaim freedom and ignite a war that will shake their world to its very roots.

Lord of the Elves | Stars: Bai Ling, Sun Korng, Srogn
